{"published time": "2024-11-15T00:00:00+08:00", "images": ["https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/image-22.png", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Foro-Imperialismo-Relidad-Censurada-4-1024x683.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Foro-Imperialismo-Relidad-Censurada-11-1024x683.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Foro-Imperialismo-Relidad-Censurada-14-1024x683.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Foro-Imperialismo-Relidad-Censurada-15-1024x683.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Foro-Imperialismo-Relidad-Censurada-21-1024x683.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Foro-Imperialismo-Relidad-Censurada-25-1024x683.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Foro-Imperialismo-Relidad-Censurada-27-1024x683.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Foro-Imperialismo-Relidad-Censurada-29-1024x683.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Foro-Imperialismo-Relidad-Censurada-31-1024x683.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Foro-Imperialismo-Relidad-Censurada-32-1024x683.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Foro-Imperialismo-Relidad-Censurada-33-1024x683.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Foro-Imperialismo-Relidad-Censurada-13-1024x683.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Arte-antiimperialista-1-1024x576.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Arte-antiimperialista-2-1024x576.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/IMG-20241115-WA0143-1024x768.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/IMG-20241115-WA0142-1024x768.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/IMG-20241115-WA0145-1024x768.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/IMG-20241115-WA0144-1024x768.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Reunion-Pro-Frente-Popular-2-1024x683.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Reunion-Pro-Frente-Popular-3-1024x683.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Reunion-Pro-Frente-Popular-8-1024x683.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Reunion-Pro-Frente-Popular-10-1024x683.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Reunion-Pro-Frente-Popular-12-1024x683.jpg", "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Reunion-Pro-Frente-Popular-16-1024x683.jpg"], "content": "<article class=\"page-content-single small single\">\n <p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-602bf2a3a0b89741bdbed123f0d11dea\">\n  La semana pasada, se llevaron a cabo importantes actividades realizadas por diversas organizaciones, en el marco del impulso de una nueva organizaci\u00f3n internacional que promueva la lucha y organizaci\u00f3n antiimperialista a nivel mundial.\n </p>\n <p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-4240bfc73dc0aa06e157020e43b1a9e9\">\n  En primer lugar, se realiz\u00f3 el foro \u201cImperialismo, vigencia de una realidad censurada\u201d. Varias organizaciones y personas expusieron ponencias que plantearon sus an\u00e1lisis sobre la situaci\u00f3n mundial y sobre el papel del imperialismo hoy en d\u00eda. Uno de los objetivos de este espacio, era volver a levantar las banderas de la lucha antiimperialista en el pa\u00eds; este permiti\u00f3 poner a la orden del d\u00eda importantes discusiones respecto al an\u00e1lisis cient\u00edfico (marxista), para comprender el sometimiento, saqueo, explotaci\u00f3n y agresiones por parte de las potencias imperialistas sobre los pueblos del tercer mundo.\n </p>\n <p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-92b5b459d8c9bebaf7f85728fe7d843a\">\n  All\u00ed se denunci\u00f3 el papel del imperialismo en las guerras de agresi\u00f3n a los pa\u00edses oprimidos, se enarbolo las resistencias de los pueblos por su liberaci\u00f3n, y se realizaron denuncias concretas de multinacionales y transnacionales a sus trabajadores, como por ejemplo, en Venezuela la empresa MASISA, que ha venido persiguiendo al trabajador Jean Mendoza por su activismo sindical.\n </p>\n <p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-35796dbada940e98e2eec0341ec76d5e\">\n  El cierre del espacio se realiz\u00f3 con la presentaci\u00f3n musical de varios luchadores y activistas revolucionarios, que con canciones antimperialistas, democr\u00e1ticas y revolucionarias, llevaron la cultura nacional y popular para elevar el esp\u00edritu de lucha y resistencia.\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n  <figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-1 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-2 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-3 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-4 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-5 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-6 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n </p>\n <p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-e271ae579075f8641200274fe3593e3f\">\n  Tambi\u00e9n, en el trascurso de la semana, fueron realizadas varias acciones de pintas antiimperialistas en la Universidad de Antioquia, instituci\u00f3n que actualmente vive un gran movimiento de lucha universitaria contra la desfinanciaci\u00f3n de la educaci\u00f3n superior p\u00fablica. En medio de las reivindicaciones universitarias, principalmente por plena financiaci\u00f3n de la universidad, algunos estudiantes han expresado la relaci\u00f3n de la problem\u00e1tica actual con las pol\u00edticas del imperialismo yanqui para Colombia, han levantado en alto la bandera del heroico pueblo palestino, y han agitado las consignas antiimperialistas en medio de la coyuntura universitaria.\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-7 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-8 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-9 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n </p>\n <p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-a4ec06de866267a253407e498e692594\">\n  Un tercer suceso, fue la realizaci\u00f3n de una importante reuni\u00f3n para avanzar en la conformaci\u00f3n de un Frente Popular Antiimperialista en el pa\u00eds. En ella participaron personas y organizaciones provenientes de diferentes regiones y ciudades como Santander, Bogot\u00e1, Medell\u00edn, Cali, y tambi\u00e9n del hermano pa\u00eds Ecuador. Hubo presencia de obreros y sindicalistas, estudiantes e intelectuales revolucionarios, organizaciones de mujeres, activistas de la lucha por la vivienda, procesos barriales, entre otros.\n </p>\n <p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-a8b4ab28f1708e8d2311a42082d80c98\">\n  En un primer momento, se discuti\u00f3 la base de unidad en torno a la cual, las organizaciones y personas all\u00ed agrupadas, comenzar\u00edan la construcci\u00f3n del Frente Popular Antiimperialista, y luego de varias horas de discusi\u00f3n, se lleg\u00f3 a unidad en 5 puntos:\n </p>\n <p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-3a2fc208786a576eb2b2c50ca1ead199\">\n  1) Lucha por la defensa y la conquista de derechos para el pueblo.\n </p>\n <p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-49c38efac7022b2365050da91d5f2e3b\">\n  2) Lucha antiimperialista e internacionalismo proletario.\n </p>\n <p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-06bd13f659e23d169971ba855beb4ba6\">\n  3) Independencia del Estado, de los gobiernos de turno y de los distintos partidos electorales.\n </p>\n <p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-5b1d7babba385652d3788bb7b03f0b46\">\n  4) Posici\u00f3n clasista y asunci\u00f3n de la lucha de clases como motor de la historia.\n </p>\n <p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-568b5bd1e4de640ccab4b484f188d91b\">\n  5) V\u00edas de hecho y movilizaci\u00f3n de las masas como forma principal de lucha.\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-10 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-11 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n </p>\n <div class=\"wp-block-group is-nowrap is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-12 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\">\n   <p class=\"IMAGE_ARCHIVED\">\n    &lt;The image of this location is in the list above, but in order to protect the site's traffic costs, it cannot be displayed here, sorry.&gt;\n   </p>\n  </figure>\n </div>\n <p>\n </p>\n <p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-065fe06fb3b747d179cf7540eb303dc2\">\n  En un segundo momento, se breg\u00f3 por plasmar la unidad alcanzada en tareas pr\u00e1cticas y concretas que dieran inicio a dicha construcci\u00f3n, como la creaci\u00f3n de un comit\u00e9 de impulso, establecer canales de comunicaci\u00f3n para las diferentes tareas, realizar acciones de apoyo a varias luchas reivindicativas y, acciones de agitaci\u00f3n y propaganda antiimperialista e internacionalista.\n </p>\n <p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-be5646e904adc944d0b0eace17bf71dc\">\n  Dos de las acciones acordadas en la reuni\u00f3n, fueron la realizaci\u00f3n de dos videos: uno en apoyo al pueblo de Valencia, Espa\u00f1a, que actualmente vive una lucha por la atenci\u00f3n al desastre vivido a causa de las inundaciones, desastre que es plena responsabilidad del Estado espa\u00f1ol, y que, ante la negligencia del mismo, las masas de Espa\u00f1a se han unido para hacer frente a la dura situaci\u00f3n. Bajo la consigna de \u201csolo el pueblo salva al pueblo\u201d en las redes sociales abundan ejemplos de organizaci\u00f3n, solidaridad popular, rechazo y combate al viejo Estado, al que las masas han denunciado como asesino por su responsabilidad en las inundaciones. Tambi\u00e9n se acord\u00f3 otro video, en apoyo a la heroica resistencia del pueblo palestino, quien con su ejemplo de coraje ha plasmado en los hechos la lucha contra el imperialismo yanqui y su lacayo sionista Israel. Estos videos los compartimos a continuaci\u00f3n.\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"360\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/T4K_PiIhUdw?feature=oembed\" title=\"Saludo al pueblo de Valencia, Espa\u00f1a\" width=\"640\">\n   </iframe>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   <iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"360\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/2Nn2w4gvgvI?feature=oembed\" title=\"Saludo a Palestina\" width=\"640\">\n   </iframe>\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n </p>\n <p class=\"has-black-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-98aae27ebec16071e905990e7edc955f\">\n  Finalmente, en un tercer momento de la reuni\u00f3n, se inici\u00f3 la socializaci\u00f3n de la propuesta para la creaci\u00f3n de la Liga Antiimperialista Internacional, importante iniciativa para que los antiimperialistas del mundo se unan en torno a la misma lucha. Se dio un inicio al debate de la propuesta que desde hace meses fue puesta a consideraci\u00f3n por el comit\u00e9 impulsor, se estableci\u00f3 la necesidad de vincular la lucha por los derechos del pueblo en Colombia con la lucha antiimperialista mundial; y, quedo el compromiso de varios luchadores por concretar e impulsar esta organizaci\u00f3n en nuestro pa\u00eds.\n </p>\n <p>\n </p>\n</article>", "pdf_content": "", "pdf_links": [], "source": "https://nuevademocracia.com.co/?p=27008", "title": "Iniciativas en Colombia en el marco del impulso de la Liga Antiimperialista Internacional", "author": "Nueva Democracia", "categories": ["_", "COLOMBIA", "INTERNACIONAL"], "source_name": "Nueva Democracia"}